{"tid":760884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】日本傳媒報道 大量中國人入侵埼玉縣 仲有狗肉賣？","createTime":"2018-07-30T02:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-07T10:01:15.000Z","uid":184679,"like":7,"dislike":115,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"5139b1092bf399ba6d697a50bce11170ef305232","tid":760884,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:46:32.000Z","msg":"其實早幾個月前已經有日本電視節目講過，今次再有報道就係話日本埼玉縣已經有大量中國人進駐，去到周圍都係普通話，周圍都係中國餐廳，話超過30間以上，而且仲有寫滿簡體字嘅理髪店、網吧&hellip;&hellip;據報道講，川口市已經有18,000中國人喺度，而且仲話有食材店有田雞同狗肉賣，唔係啩？真係聞者傷心，收手啦好嘛。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.gameover.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/17165651/9dc874af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gameover.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F17165651%2F9dc874af.jpg&h=7b3fb9ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.gameover.com.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/17165647/20180716-00000003-pseven-000-3-view.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.gameover.com.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F17165647%2F20180716-00000003-pseven-000-3-view.jpg&h=cb75087e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.teepr.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/07/949255-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teepr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F07%2F949255-XXL.jpg&h=7de8c937&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iswP7Y57J1c#action=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DiswP7Y57J1c%23action%3Dshare&d=bAgHhObGkLxSANTR6DeyJwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=ddeb5694\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iswP7Y57J1c#action=share</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gameover.com.hk/?p=410229\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gameover.com.hk%2F%3Fp%3D410229&d=bAgHhObGkLxSANTR6DeyJwhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=6ac4c86b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gameover.com.hk/?p=410229</a>"},{"pid":"3cde730c2c752d7af6df17c38fd09d47a5f68465","tid":760884,"uid":11962,"like":53,"dislike":1,"score":52,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:47:17.000Z","msg":"屌，日本都淪陷"},{"pid":"6c3f3fc5d92e92fdb4a6a9f3fbb62e83eefe91e6","tid":760884,"uid":98386,"like":104,"dislike":4,"score":100,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:48:22.000Z","msg":"就咁睇圖以為係支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bdbf4b96340bcc010d0cb9efc41e15b4aeb15c35","tid":760884,"uid":11962,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"6c3f3fc5d92e92fdb4a6a9f3fbb62e83eefe91e6","tid":760884,"uid":98386,"like":104,"dislike":4,"score":100,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:48:22.000Z","msg":"就咁睇圖以為係支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T02:48:58.000Z","msg":"支那人去邊都搞小圈子果下衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb94163e38f2f73a1998f3e87e23902cd9eeadc9","tid":760884,"uid":79959,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:00:01.000Z","msg":"大阪道頓堀東端<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"246c78b056486e1219c745a95ed1aa359f4d034e","tid":760884,"uid":58552,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:02:52.000Z","msg":"嘩屌 <br />\n個格同支國無分別"},{"pid":"5da10e0fa00305e402c0f1e5647aa2f960a8a332","tid":760884,"uid":44454,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:09:46.000Z","msg":"咁係好事，再嚴重啲會激起民憤，右翼抬頭"},{"pid":"9fadbb9758a5194b729213dbfd333c6f5bd14717","tid":760884,"uid":20241,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:10:06.000Z","msg":"由其川味鴨頭個張相<br />\n直頭朕支那味出曬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c242932d70b5535ab6fba0ecb12b3c16489cbd2f","tid":760884,"uid":61675,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T03:11:52.000Z","msg":"地球既大毒瘤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/de